title: Iron Maiden DLC for Rocksmith 2014
description:
This torrent contains the Iron Maiden dlc for Rocksmith 2014.

To install this dlc:

- Copy the files from the .rar into your dlc folder (default location: C:Program Files(x86)UbisoftRocksmith 2014dlc)

- Add the following IDs to your 'skidrow.ini' file, located in your Rocksmith 2014 root folder.

17=258348
18=258349
19=258350
20=258351
21=258352

Enjoy the dlc!
